text: This sign is amazing. Hey guys. Welcome to my Contiki

Contiki tour, from Cairns all the way down the east coast to

Sydney. So why not start of with a 
 bang. We are here at the
A.J Hackett (I know you guys love this) Bungy site here in

Okay, so there is two different things you can do here at AJ
Hackett bungy site: there is bungy and there is the Minjin Swing
which is the fasted rainforest swing in the world.
Man: Are you scared? Nadine: No. Minjin swing!
That was awesome. That was really good. Ahh, you can't see

That's how high that was. I was having a freak out moment up

there, because I did not now it was 
 going to be parallel, but it
was. I'm glad I did it, because it was really fun.

 go from 1 to 5, that is
